 <span data-ttu-id="f5e81-102">使用中的接口<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation?displayProperty=nameWithType>命名空间以启用远程对象的访问类型信息的组件，而无直接访问<xref:System.Type>的远程对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f5e81-102">Use the interfaces in the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace to enable components to access type information for a remote object without having direct access to the <xref:System.Type> of the remote object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f5e81-103"><xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation?displayProperty=nameWithType>命名空间定义反射功能，用于使用接口和结构中的组件<xref:System.AddIn.Contract?displayProperty=nameWithType>， <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation?displayProperty=nameWithType>，和<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections?displayProperty=nameWithType>命名空间进行通信。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f5e81-103">The <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace defines reflection functionality for components that use the interfaces and structures in the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation?displayProperty=nameWithType>, and <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespaces to communicate.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f5e81-104">这些命名空间中的接口也称为约定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f5e81-104">The interfaces in these namespaces are also called contracts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f5e81-105">所有协定都派生<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract>接口。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f5e81-105">All contracts derive from the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract> interface.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f5e81-106">当使用约定来管理组件之间的通信，您必须实现<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract>接口中公开给其他组件的类型信息的类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f5e81-106">When using contracts to manage the communication between components, you must implement the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract> interface in a type to expose the type information to other components.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f5e81-107">组件可以通过调用然后访问该类型的成员<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract.GetRemoteType%2A>方法的接口，用于获取<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f5e81-107">Components can then access the members of the type by calling the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract.GetRemoteType%2A> method of the interface to get an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f5e81-108">其他接口和结构中<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation?displayProperty=nameWithType>命名空间提供的类型的委托、 属性、 方法、 事件和字段的信息的访问权限。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f5e81-108">The other interfaces and structures in the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace provide access to type information for delegates, properties, methods, events, and fields.</span></span>  
  
